Happy Birthday

Beautiful Prakriti

I Love You

Dear Prakriti,

       Happy Birthday to you!
       Happy Birthday to you!

    You are my happiness, my joy,
   and my sunshine in every way.

  On this special day, I wish you all
   the best things life can give.
  May your heart be filled with joy,
   and may you always feel loved.

   I hope your day brings laughter,
  and sweet moments to treasure.
   You deserve all the happiness
  that you could ever measure.

    You light up my life in every way.
   I am so thankful for you each day.
  Lets make more memories together,
  and enjoy every moment, come what may.

   You are special, a true gift to me,
    your love fills my heart with glee.
   Today, lets celebrate your life,
  and all the joy you bring, cant you see?

   May your dreams soar high and true,
  and every wish you make come through.
   I promise to stand by your side,
  and support you in all you do.

    Heres to you, my love,
      on this special day so bright!
   May your heart be filled with joy,
  and your future be a beautiful sight.

   Enjoy your day to the fullest, my dear!
   Ill always be here, never fear.
   Happy Birthday!
